{
  "video_id": "hv-tFIuhD8E",
  "title": "What it feels like to see Earth from space | Benjamin Grant",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12962.0,
      "end_time": 16180.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s Christmas Eve, 1968."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17340.0,
      "end_time": 20756.0,
      "text": "The Apollo 8 spacecraft has successfully completed"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20780.0,
      "end_time": 23500.0,
      "text": "its first three orbits around the moon."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24780.0,
      "end_time": 27476.0,
      "text": "Launched from Cape Canaveral three days before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27500.0,
      "end_time": 29196.0,
      "text": "this is the first time"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29220.0,
      "end_time": 32940.0,
      "text": "that humans have ever traveled beyond low Earth orbit."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 34260.0,
      "end_time": 36275.0,
      "text": "On the vessel&#39;s fourth pass,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 36300.0,
      "end_time": 38995.0,
      "text": "the Earth slowly comes into view"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 39200.0,
      "end_time": 41980.0,
      "text": "and reveals itself above the Moon&#39;s horizon."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 43500.0,
      "end_time": 47436.0,
      "text": "Astronaut Bill Anders frantically asks his crewmates where their camera is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 47460.0,
      "end_time": 49876.0,
      "text": "grabs the Hasselblad, points it towards the window,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 49900.0,
      "end_time": 51236.0,
      "text": "presses the shutter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 51260.0,
      "end_time": 55379.0,
      "text": "and takes one of the most important photographs of all time:"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 56380.0,
      "end_time": 57580.0,
      "text": "\"Earthrise.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 58540.0,
      "end_time": 61196.0,
      "text": "When the crew was safely home a few days later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 61220.0,
      "end_time": 62839.0,
      "text": "they were asked about the mission."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 63780.0,
      "end_time": 66360.0,
      "text": "Anders famously replied,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 66600.0,
      "end_time": 68156.0,
      "text": "\"We went to the moon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 68180.0,
      "end_time": 71380.0,
      "text": "but we actually discovered Earth.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 73300.0,
      "end_time": 76860.0,
      "text": "What did he and his fellow crewmates feel"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 77620.0,
      "end_time": 79600.0,
      "text": "in this incredible moment?"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 79660.0,
      "end_time": 82196.0,
      "text": "In a study released just this past year,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 82220.0,
      "end_time": 85276.0,
      "text": "a team of researchers at the University of Pennsylvania"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 85300.0,
      "end_time": 88916.0,
      "text": "examined the testimonies of hundreds of astronauts"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 88940.0,
      "end_time": 92196.0,
      "text": "who had the opportunity to view the Earth from space."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 92220.0,
      "end_time": 95220.0,
      "text": "Their analysis uncovered three common feelings:"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 96200.0,
      "end_time": 99795.0,
      "text": "first, a greater appreciation for Earth&#39;s beauty;"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 99820.0,
      "end_time": 104916.0,
      "text": "second, an increased sense of connection to all other living beings;"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 104940.0,
      "end_time": 110300.0,
      "text": "and third, an unexpected, often overwhelming sense of emotion."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 110980.0,
      "end_time": 114436.0,
      "text": "The researchers believe that seeing the Earth from a great distance"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 114460.0,
      "end_time": 118395.0,
      "text": "provokes someone to develop new cognitive frameworks"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 118420.0,
      "end_time": 120100.0,
      "text": "to understand what they are seeing."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 121600.0,
      "end_time": 124360.0,
      "text": "They believe these astronauts were forever changed"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 124600.0,
      "end_time": 125916.0,
      "text": "by this new view,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 125940.0,
      "end_time": 127836.0,
      "text": "this new perspective,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 127860.0,
      "end_time": 130100.0,
      "text": "this new visual truth."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 131180.0,
      "end_time": 135540.0,
      "text": "This feeling is commonly referred to as the \"overview effect.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 136940.0,
      "end_time": 141180.0,
      "text": "Only 558 people have ever been to outer space."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 142190.0,
      "end_time": 145156.0,
      "text": "558 people had the opportunity"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 145180.0,
      "end_time": 148316.0,
      "text": "to gaze down in awe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 148340.0,
      "end_time": 149996.0,
      "text": "to wonder at our planet"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 150200.0,
      "end_time": 153636.0,
      "text": "floating in an infinite sea of darkness."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 153660.0,
      "end_time": 156436.0,
      "text": "But what if that number were bigger?"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 156460.0,
      "end_time": 159956.0,
      "text": "Three years ago, I set off on my own mission:"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 159980.0,
      "end_time": 164715.0,
      "text": "to see if I could bring this feeling of overwhelming scale and beauty"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 164740.0,
      "end_time": 166396.0,
      "text": "to many more people"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 166420.0,
      "end_time": 168476.0,
      "text": "just by using one small computer"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 168500.0,
      "end_time": 170700.0,
      "text": "in my small New York City apartment."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 171300.0,
      "end_time": 175316.0,
      "text": "It was then, in 2013, that I launched \"Daily Overview.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 175340.0,
      "end_time": 178876.0,
      "text": "Every day, I have used satellite imagery"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 178900.0,
      "end_time": 183276.0,
      "text": "to create one expansive overhead view of our planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 183300.0,
      "end_time": 188236.0,
      "text": "More than 1,000 of these images have been created thus far,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 188260.0,
      "end_time": 190756.0,
      "text": "and more than 600,000 people"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 190780.0,
      "end_time": 193836.0,
      "text": "tune in for this daily dose of perspectives."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 193860.0,
      "end_time": 198956.0,
      "text": "I create the imagery by curating photos from the massive archive"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 198980.0,
      "end_time": 201340.0,
      "text": "of a satellite company called Digital Globe."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 201900.0,
      "end_time": 204676.0,
      "text": "They operate a constellation of five satellites,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 204700.0,
      "end_time": 207316.0,
      "text": "each roughly the size of an ambulance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 207340.0,
      "end_time": 209756.0,
      "text": "that is constantly taking pictures of the Earth"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 209780.0,
      "end_time": 214100.0,
      "text": "as they orbit at 28,000 kilometers per hour."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 215100.0,
      "end_time": 216660.0,
      "text": "Now, what does this mean?"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 217420.0,
      "end_time": 219796.0,
      "text": "Each of these satellites is equipped with a camera"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 219820.0,
      "end_time": 222715.0,
      "text": "that has a focal length of 16 meters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 222740.0,
      "end_time": 226436.0,
      "text": "so that&#39;s roughly 290 times greater"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 226460.0,
      "end_time": 230780.0,
      "text": "than a DSLR camera equipped with a standard 55 millimeter lens."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 231620.0,
      "end_time": 234760.0,
      "text": "So if were able to attach one of their satellites"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 234100.0,
      "end_time": 236260.0,
      "text": "to the roof of this theater in Oxford,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 237200.0,
      "end_time": 239796.0,
      "text": "we could take a picture of a football,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 239820.0,
      "end_time": 243900.0,
      "text": "clearly, on the pitch at the stadium in Amsterdam."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 244860.0,
      "end_time": 247420.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s 450 kilometers away."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 248380.0,
      "end_time": 251316.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s incredibly powerful technology."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 251340.0,
      "end_time": 253836.0,
      "text": "And I decided at the beginning of this project"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 253860.0,
      "end_time": 256316.0,
      "text": "that I would use that incredible technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 256339.0,
      "end_time": 258236.0,
      "text": "to focus on the places"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 258260.0,
      "end_time": 260579.0,
      "text": "where humans have impacted the planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 261940.0,
      "end_time": 266316.0,
      "text": "As a species, we dig and scrape the Earth for resources,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 266340.0,
      "end_time": 267780.0,
      "text": "we produce energy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 268500.0,
      "end_time": 272200.0,
      "text": "we raise animals and cultivate crops for food,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 272700.0,
      "end_time": 275156.0,
      "text": "we build cities, we move around,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 275180.0,
      "end_time": 276516.0,
      "text": "we create waste."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 276540.0,
      "end_time": 279836.0,
      "text": "And in the process of doing all of these things,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 279860.0,
      "end_time": 282956.0,
      "text": "we shape landscapes and seascapes"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 282980.0,
      "end_time": 286940.0,
      "text": "and cityscapes with increasing control and impunity."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 288460.0,
      "end_time": 289715.0,
      "text": "So with that in mind,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 289740.0,
      "end_time": 292420.0,
      "text": "I would like to share a few of my overviews with you now."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 293500.0,
      "end_time": 296996.0,
      "text": "Here we see cargo ships and oil tankers"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 297200.0,
      "end_time": 299780.0,
      "text": "waiting outside the entry to the port of Singapore."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 300700.0,
      "end_time": 305635.0,
      "text": "This facility is the second-busiest in the world by terms of total tonnage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 305660.0,
      "end_time": 309360.0,
      "text": "accounting for one-fifth of the world&#39;s shipping containers"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 309600.0,
      "end_time": 311516.0,
      "text": "and one half of the annual supply"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 311540.0,
      "end_time": 312900.0,
      "text": "of crude oil."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 313620.0,
      "end_time": 317516.0,
      "text": "If you look closely at this overview, you&#39;ll see a lot of little specks."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 317540.0,
      "end_time": 320396.0,
      "text": "Those are actually cows at a feedlot"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 320420.0,
      "end_time": 322940.0,
      "text": "in Summerfield, Texas, in the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 323900.0,
      "end_time": 326116.0,
      "text": "So once cows reach a particular weight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 326140.0,
      "end_time": 328276.0,
      "text": "roughly 300 kilograms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 328300.0,
      "end_time": 331100.0,
      "text": "they are moved here and placed on a specialized diet."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 331780.0,
      "end_time": 336916.0,
      "text": "Over the next three to four months, the cows gain an additional 180 kilograms"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 336940.0,
      "end_time": 339760.0,
      "text": "before they are shipped off to slaughter."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 339100.0,
      "end_time": 342516.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re also probably wondering about this glowing pool at the top there."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 342540.0,
      "end_time": 346396.0,
      "text": "That gets its color from a unique combination of manure, chemicals"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 346420.0,
      "end_time": 349460.0,
      "text": "and a particular type of algae that grows in the stagnant water."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 350980.0,
      "end_time": 353796.0,
      "text": "This is the Mount Whaleback iron ore mine"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 353820.0,
      "end_time": 357116.0,
      "text": "in the Pilbara region of Western Australia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 357140.0,
      "end_time": 360955.0,
      "text": "a beautiful yet scary scar on the face of the Earth."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 360980.0,
      "end_time": 363360.0,
      "text": "Of the world&#39;s mined iron ore,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 363600.0,
      "end_time": 365996.0,
      "text": "98 percent is used to make steel"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 366200.0,
      "end_time": 369316.0,
      "text": "and is therefore a major component in the construction of buildings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 369340.0,
      "end_time": 373340.0,
      "text": "automobiles or appliances such as your dishwasher or refrigerator."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 375600.0,
      "end_time": 377940.0,
      "text": "This is a solar concentrator in Seville, Spain."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 378700.0,
      "end_time": 383396.0,
      "text": "So this facility contains 2,650 mirrors"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 383420.0,
      "end_time": 388476.0,
      "text": "which are arrayed in concentric circles around an 140-meter-tall tower"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 388500.0,
      "end_time": 389740.0,
      "text": "at its center."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 390300.0,
      "end_time": 391756.0,
      "text": "At the top of the tower,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 391780.0,
      "end_time": 393996.0,
      "text": "there is a capsule of molten salt"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 394200.0,
      "end_time": 397635.0,
      "text": "that gets heated by the beams of light reflected upwards"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 397660.0,
      "end_time": 398980.0,
      "text": "from the mirrors below."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 399620.0,
      "end_time": 403760.0,
      "text": "From there, the salt circulates to a storage tank underground,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 403100.0,
      "end_time": 404556.0,
      "text": "where it produces steam,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 404580.0,
      "end_time": 406360.0,
      "text": "which spins turbines"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 406600.0,
      "end_time": 409556.0,
      "text": "and generates enough electricity to power 70,000 homes"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 409580.0,
      "end_time": 413900.0,
      "text": "and offsets 30,000 tons of carbon dioxide emissions every year."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 415200.0,
      "end_time": 419360.0,
      "text": "This overview shows deforestation in Santa Cruz, Bolivia"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 419600.0,
      "end_time": 422940.0,
      "text": "immediately adjacent to untouched tracts of rainforest."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 424320.0,
      "end_time": 426556.0,
      "text": "Deforestation in the country has primarily been driven"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 426580.0,
      "end_time": 429195.0,
      "text": "by the expansion of mechanized agriculture"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 429220.0,
      "end_time": 430876.0,
      "text": "and cattle ranching,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 430900.0,
      "end_time": 434116.0,
      "text": "so as the country tries to meet the demand of its growing population"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 434140.0,
      "end_time": 435356.0,
      "text": "and feed them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 435380.0,
      "end_time": 437676.0,
      "text": "the sacrificial destruction of its rainforest"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 437700.0,
      "end_time": 439180.0,
      "text": "has taken place to do so."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 439980.0,
      "end_time": 444956.0,
      "text": "It is estimated that the country lost 4.5 million acres of rainforest"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 444980.0,
      "end_time": 446436.0,
      "text": "in one decade alone"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 446460.0,
      "end_time": 448659.0,
      "text": "from 2000 until 2010."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 449740.0,
      "end_time": 452660.0,
      "text": "This is the Eixample district in Barcelona, Spain."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 453460.0,
      "end_time": 456236.0,
      "text": "So the overview perspective can be incredibly helpful"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 456260.0,
      "end_time": 458276.0,
      "text": "to help us understand how cities function"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 458300.0,
      "end_time": 461236.0,
      "text": "and how we can devise smarter solutions for urban planning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 461260.0,
      "end_time": 463396.0,
      "text": "and this will become only more relevant"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 463420.0,
      "end_time": 468916.0,
      "text": "as it is expected that 4.9 billion people will live in cities around the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 468940.0,
      "end_time": 470180.0,
      "text": "by the year 2030."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 471600.0,
      "end_time": 475276.0,
      "text": "This area of Barcelona is characterized by its strict grid pattern,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 475300.0,
      "end_time": 477316.0,
      "text": "apartments with communal courtyards"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 477340.0,
      "end_time": 479515.0,
      "text": "and these octagonal intersections"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 479540.0,
      "end_time": 482556.0,
      "text": "which allow for more sunlight, better ventilation"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 482580.0,
      "end_time": 484460.0,
      "text": "and additional parking at street level."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 485300.0,
      "end_time": 489740.0,
      "text": "And here we see that grid pattern but under much different circumstances."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 490300.0,
      "end_time": 493796.0,
      "text": "This is the Dadaab Refugee Camp in northern Kenya,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 493820.0,
      "end_time": 496756.0,
      "text": "the largest such facility of its kind in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 496780.0,
      "end_time": 500350.0,
      "text": "To cope with the influx of refugees who are fleeing Somalia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 500600.0,
      "end_time": 501956.0,
      "text": "where there is famine and conflict,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 501980.0,
      "end_time": 504476.0,
      "text": "the UN has built this area gridded out at left"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 504500.0,
      "end_time": 506236.0,
      "text": "called the LFO extension"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 506260.0,
      "end_time": 507796.0,
      "text": "to house more and more refugees"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 507820.0,
      "end_time": 510796.0,
      "text": "who are arriving and occupying these white dots,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 510820.0,
      "end_time": 512155.0,
      "text": "which are actually tents"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 512179.0,
      "end_time": 514659.0,
      "text": "which will slowly fill up the area over time."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 515299.0,
      "end_time": 518395.0,
      "text": "So if you have one of these overviews,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 518419.0,
      "end_time": 520219.0,
      "text": "you have a moment in time."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 521100.0,
      "end_time": 522956.0,
      "text": "If we have two overviews, however,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 522980.0,
      "end_time": 525820.0,
      "text": "we are able to tell stories about changes in time."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 526580.0,
      "end_time": 528916.0,
      "text": "I call that feature of the project \"Juxtapose,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 528940.0,
      "end_time": 531300.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;ll share a few examples of it with you now."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 532600.0,
      "end_time": 536380.0,
      "text": "So the tulip fields in Netherlands bloom every year in April."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 536940.0,
      "end_time": 540760.0,
      "text": "So we take an image captured in March a few weeks before"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 540100.0,
      "end_time": 542620.0,
      "text": "and contrast it to one taken a few weeks later."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 543380.0,
      "end_time": 547820.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re able to watch the flowers bloom in this magnificent cascade of color."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 548860.0,
      "end_time": 554260.0,
      "text": "It is estimated that the Dutch produce 4.3 billion tulip bulbs every year."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 555980.0,
      "end_time": 559760.0,
      "text": "In 2015, two dams collapsed"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 559100.0,
      "end_time": 561796.0,
      "text": "at an iron ore mine in southeastern Brazil,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 561820.0,
      "end_time": 564436.0,
      "text": "causing one of the worst environmental disasters"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 564460.0,
      "end_time": 565889.0,
      "text": "in the history of the country."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 566300.0,
      "end_time": 570195.0,
      "text": "It is estimated that 62 million cubic meters of waste"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 570220.0,
      "end_time": 571916.0,
      "text": "were released when the dams broke,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 571940.0,
      "end_time": 574356.0,
      "text": "destroying numerous villages in the process,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 574380.0,
      "end_time": 577380.0,
      "text": "including Bento Rodrigues, seen here before ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 579940.0,
      "end_time": 581780.0,
      "text": "and after the flood."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 583100.0,
      "end_time": 586636.0,
      "text": "Ultimately, 19 people were killed in this disaster."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 586660.0,
      "end_time": 589756.0,
      "text": "Half a million people did not have access to clean drinking water"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 589780.0,
      "end_time": 591795.0,
      "text": "for an extended period of time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 591820.0,
      "end_time": 594276.0,
      "text": "and the waste soon entered into the Doce River,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 594300.0,
      "end_time": 596795.0,
      "text": "extended for 650 kilometers"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 596820.0,
      "end_time": 598476.0,
      "text": "all the way into the sea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 598500.0,
      "end_time": 602300.0,
      "text": "killing unknowable amounts of plant and animal life along the way."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 603260.0,
      "end_time": 607360.0,
      "text": "And lastly, here is a story related to the crisis in Syria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 607600.0,
      "end_time": 610915.0,
      "text": "a conflict which has claimed the lives of hundreds of thousands of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 610940.0,
      "end_time": 612260.0,
      "text": "and displaced millions."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 612860.0,
      "end_time": 617356.0,
      "text": "So this patch of desert is seen in Mafraq, Jordan in 2011,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 617380.0,
      "end_time": 619760.0,
      "text": "the year the conflict started,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 619100.0,
      "end_time": 623740.0,
      "text": "and when we compare it to an image captured just this year in 2017,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 624540.0,
      "end_time": 627140.0,
      "text": "we see the construction of the Zaatari refugee camp."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 627860.0,
      "end_time": 631516.0,
      "text": "So just as the astronauts of Apollo 8"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 631540.0,
      "end_time": 635476.0,
      "text": "watched the Earth rising above the lunar landscape for the first time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 635500.0,
      "end_time": 637676.0,
      "text": "there is no way that you could have imagined"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 637700.0,
      "end_time": 641860.0,
      "text": "what the places I just showed you look like from outer space."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 642540.0,
      "end_time": 645236.0,
      "text": "And while you may enjoy the aesthetics of an image,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 645260.0,
      "end_time": 647516.0,
      "text": "once you learn exactly what it is you&#39;re seeing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 647540.0,
      "end_time": 650420.0,
      "text": "you may struggle with the fact that you still like it."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 651300.0,
      "end_time": 654116.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s the tension I want to create with my work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 654140.0,
      "end_time": 657276.0,
      "text": "because I believe it is that contemplation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 657300.0,
      "end_time": 659236.0,
      "text": "that internal dialogue"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 659260.0,
      "end_time": 661676.0,
      "text": "that will lead to greater interest in our planet"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 661700.0,
      "end_time": 663940.0,
      "text": "and more awareness of what we&#39;re doing to it."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 664780.0,
      "end_time": 667716.0,
      "text": "I believe that viewing the Earth from the overview perspective"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 667740.0,
      "end_time": 670580.0,
      "text": "is more important now than ever before."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 671260.0,
      "end_time": 674596.0,
      "text": "Through the incredible technology of these high-flying cameras,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 674620.0,
      "end_time": 677796.0,
      "text": "we can see, monitor and expose"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 677820.0,
      "end_time": 680220.0,
      "text": "the unprecedented impact that we are having."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 681180.0,
      "end_time": 683195.0,
      "text": "And whether we are scientists"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 683220.0,
      "end_time": 686236.0,
      "text": "or engineers or policymakers"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 686260.0,
      "end_time": 688460.0,
      "text": "or investors or artists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 689220.0,
      "end_time": 692676.0,
      "text": "if we can adopt a more expansive perspective,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 692700.0,
      "end_time": 695996.0,
      "text": "embrace the truth of what is going on"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 696200.0,
      "end_time": 699260.0,
      "text": "and contemplate the long-term health of our planet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 700180.0,
      "end_time": 702156.0,
      "text": "we will create a better"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 702180.0,
      "end_time": 704955.0,
      "text": "and safer and smarter future"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 704980.0,
      "end_time": 707116.0,
      "text": "for our one and only home."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 707140.0,
      "end_time": 708356.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 708380.0,
      "end_time": 712700.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}